data.description: Welcome to this Immaculate Renovated Home featuring new plumbing, electrical, HVAC, new windows, and a HUGE lot. This semi-detached home boasts plenty of windows throughout pouring in natural light. The sleek, new kitchen has plenty of cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, and tiled backsplash. From the kitchen, step out onto your impressive deck designed for dinners al fresco or outdoor entertaining. The upper level hosts two sunlit bedrooms and a new hallway bathroom making this home move-in ready. Journey to the finished, walkout lower level that has a flexible space that can be used as a 3rd bedroom, in-law suite, or family room with a full bathroom.  Access the incredible backyard space from the lower level. The washer and dryer combo in the kitchen makes everyday living a breeze. There is an extra washer and dryer hookup in the basement. Walking distance to Deanwood Community Center. Close to public transportation and just minutes to 295.
